Monarch Capital corp saidits board has called its convertible preferred stock forredemption on May Eight.    The company said shareholders may exchange the preferredshares for shares of new nonconvertible preferred stock with adividend of five dlrs to 6.40 dlrs per share, convert them intocommon stock at a rate of 0.8 common share for each preferredshare or allow the preferred to be redeemed for 46.51 dlrs pershare. Reuter&#3;